Package: caja-pdf-optimizer
Version: 3.6.3
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: caja, imagemagick, ghostscript, poppler-utils, libnotify-bin, libreoffice, bash, caja-extensions-common, caja-actions
Maintainer: Dom <user@localhost>
Description: Professional PDF Optimizer Suite for Caja (v3.6.3 LTS)
 The Ultimate PDF Compression & Conversion Tool for MATE Desktop Environment.
 .
 Changes in v3.6.3:
  - Critical fix: Added 'poppler-utils' to mandatory dependencies (required for pdfinfo/pdfseparate).
  - Improved menu compatibility: Dual registration in /usr/share/file-manager/actions and /usr/share/caja-actions.
  - Cosmetic: Updated versioning in installation logs.
 Changes in v3.6.2:
  - Fixed "cache resources exhausted" error by increasing ImageMagick memory limits.
  - Scientific "Trellis-Quantization Mimic" applied to ALL DPI modes.
  - Added support for MS Word (.docx, .doc) and ODT files.
  - Implemented Camouflage Mode for privacy.
  - Portable-like standalone architecture for Linux.
